    "Stakeholders should specify the population they want to generalize to and use corresponding vignettes for evaluations.",
    "This study has several limitations.",
    "First, we could not obtain additional information for these cases.",
    "Although this is also a common issue with traditional vignettes, having extra details available that SAAs might inquire about would be beneficial.",
